description: This file defines the TargetGroup class for managing AWS Elastic Load Balancer target groups, including methods for creating, reading, updating, and deleting target groups using AWS SDK.

classes.name: TargetGroup
classes.description: Represents an AWS Elastic Load Balancer Target Group with methods to create, read, update, and delete the resource.

methods.name: _create
methods.description: Creates the AWS Target Group using provided configuration and AWS API client.

methods.name: _read
methods.description: Reads and retrieves the current state of the AWS Target Group.

methods.name: _update
methods.description: Updates the AWS Target Group with new configuration.

methods.name: get_arn
methods.description: Retrieves the ARN of the Target Group.
